name: COVID-19 data
title: COVID-19 data
description: Every 15 minutes updated statistic about Coronavirus. Latest stats by country, are collected from several reliable sources. You can also see total stats and daily reports. With 6 servers around the world, we are also fastest API related with COVID-19 on RapidAPI marketplace.

endpoints.name: getDailyReportTotals
endpoints.description: Get daily report data for the whole world. Date format is by [ISO 8601](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601) standard, but you can provide different format with date-format parameter. If you don't provide the `date` parameter, the whole timeline will be returned.

endpoints.name: getLatestAllCountries
endpoints.description: Get latest data for all countries.

endpoints.name: getLatestTotals
endpoints.description: Get latest data for whole world.
